I'm grateful, but I hope she doesn't for now.

8
00:00:25,050 --> 00:00:26,070
It's Aeji.

9
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:27,840
Miho is...

10
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:31,540
It's nothing.

11
00:00:37,650 --> 00:00:38,870
Let me see.

12
00:00:42,510 --> 00:00:43,940
I have something to tell you.

13
00:00:43,950 --> 00:00:45,560
Go ahead.

14
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,440
Don't be surprised.

15
