16
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,260
What's he doing?

17
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,840
It's Mr. Ko.

18
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,590
Please open the door.

19
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,900
Huh?

20
00:01:59,810 --> 00:02:01,470
How...

21
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,440
